1. To compile, make CUDA.
2. A tmp folder is created before compiling. All vtk files are stored in this location.
3. There are 4 scenarios that have been provided for test. Respective .par and .in files are already included in the package.
4  To run stable: make run1
5  To run repell: make run2
6. To run attract: make run3
7. To run block: make run4
8. To clean. make clean. executable hespa is deleted. and tmp folder is deleted.
9. To run ./hespa parafile.par
10. Make sure the folder tmp is created before running again. 
